    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "大家好 我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 34.48,
    "end": 38.14,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們請把注意力集中過來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 38.34,
    "end": 41.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "今天要破解電阻大魔王",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 41.98,
    "end": 45.46,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師講義右邊畫了三種形狀",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 45.66,
    "end": 48.91,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "它們的長度明明都一模一樣",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 49.11,
    "end": 52.05,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "到底哪一個的電阻最大啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 52.25,
    "end": 56.0,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "我們想像自己正在馬路上奔跑",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 56.2,
    "end": 59.76,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "如果是一條又粗又短的馬路",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 59.96,
    "end": 63.09,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "跑起來當然超級輕鬆啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 63.29,
    "end": 68.53,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 輕鬆就代表電阻非常小",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 68.73,
    "end": 72.7,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "反過來說路如果越窄而且越長",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 72.9,
    "end": 76.31,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "跑起來就會越痛苦越費力",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 76.51,
    "end": 80.94,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "喔 所以那個三角柱最扁最窄",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 81.14,
    "end": 84.26,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "它的電阻一定就是最大的",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 84.46,
    "end": 88.89,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "漂亮 觀念完全正確喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 89.09,
    "end": 101.17,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "① $R \\propto \\frac{L}{A}$",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "① $R \\propto \\frac{L}{A}$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 93.93,
    "end": 97.97,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們 趕快把最窄的圈起來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 101.17,
    "end": 104.92,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師講義上面還有四個小重點",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 105.12,
    "end": 109.04,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "第一個 銀的導電性是最好的",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 109.24,
    "end": 112.94,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "第二點說電器串聯會越接越長",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 113.14,
    "end": 116.54,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "所以總電阻就會跟著變大囉",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 116.74,
    "end": 121.88,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 就像馬路被無限拉長一樣",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 122.08,
    "end": 125.64,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "第三點說並聯就像是開分身",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 125.84,
    "end": 129.09,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "馬路變寬了總電阻就變小",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 129.29,
    "end": 131.17,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "答對了 戰士們記住這個並聯",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 131.37,
    "end": 138.9,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "② 串聯電阻變大， 並聯電阻變小",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "② 串聯電阻變大， 並聯電阻變小"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 138.9,
    "end": 142.31,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接著把視線移到講義的左邊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 142.51,
    "end": 146.07,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師 這題真的太經典了啦",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 146.27,
    "end": 149.28,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "開關 $S$ 只要一按下去",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": [
      "$S$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 149.48,
    "end": 152.63,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "電路到底會發生什麼事啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 152.83,
    "end": 156.61,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒按下去前電流只有兩條路",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 156.81,
    "end": 160.39,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "把開關 $S$ 順利按下去之後",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": [
      "$S$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 160.59,
    "end": 165.02,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇 瞬間多開了一條路出來耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 165.22,
    "end": 168.8,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "三條路並聯代表馬路變寬了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 169.0,
    "end": 172.44,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "總電阻就會在一瞬間變小",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 172.64,
    "end": 176.06,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "既然整條馬路變得更好走了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 176.26,
    "end": 179.46,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "總電流就會瘋狂地大爆衝",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 179.66,
    "end": 200.41,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "③ $\\text{多開並聯} \\rightarrow \\text{總電阻小， 電流大}$",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "③ $\\text{多開並聯} \\rightarrow \\text{總電阻小， 電流大}$"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 184.4,
    "end": 188.75,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "喔 所以安培計上面測的讀數",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 188.95,
    "end": 192.06,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就會變得越來越大對不對",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 192.26,
    "end": 197.21,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 陷阱完全被你破解了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
